                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": ":plc:j7nm3lrd5h7fm3sfhcv3lhfv\/dev.lopecode.bundle\/3mkjwz5coof2w`",
                                "style": {
                                    "code": true
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "  ?\n\nYes its an SPA, but its also on the atmosphere. It is two manifestations of the same thing. Thats heirarchical thinking, when you try to put something in one box or another in a mutually exclusive way. Both places contain the same code base. It is not exclusively an SPA, but it can be an SPA if presented that way.\n\n\"but weird from a UX point of view\" this is a prototype, its not been refined at all, its just a conversation about a technical possability, not a final thing."
